snippet.title: JETT: The Far Shore - Reveal Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description: JETT: The Far Shore invites you on an interstellar trip to carve out a future for a people haunted by oblivion in this cinematic action adventure coming Holiday 2020 on the PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4.
